        "created_at": "2020-11-24T03:47:08.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Buzz - hold onto that bottle. I\u2019m sitting on a lot of Ruchottes from that era as well as some Vergers. Let\u2019s pop em together after this pesky COVID thing sorts out. I\u2019m afraid many of these may be a bit bit weak in the knees, but there could be some revelatory surprises as well. BTW, All of my Seagrams labels are as yours. Only the grey market labels add the premier or grand cru designation.</p>",
